results.name: a(n) = n OR 8n, where OR is bitwise OR.
comment: Perhaps this is a rearrangement of A114386?
No, e.g., a(513) = 4617 is not in A114386.  Moreover, this sequence is not injective, as a(65) = a(73) = 585. - _Robert Israel_, Jan 31 2021
